!scripts/coverage/

# Individual package lockfiles (use root pnpm-lock.yaml only)
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
!pnpm-lock.yaml

# Claude Code session metadata (worktrees, memory, jobs)
.claude/
